// bench/bench.hexa — Dual-Phi Consciousness Benchmark
// Source: bench/bench.py (4267 LOC)
// Phase 5: structural port. PyTorch/numpy ops -> TODO comments.
// Runtime implementation stays in bench.py; this file is the canonical
// architectural spec (thresholds, structs, verification conditions, CLI).
//
// Usage:
//   hexa bench/bench.hexa --verify
//   hexa bench/bench.hexa --phi-only
//   hexa bench/bench.hexa --training
//   hexa bench/bench.hexa --compare
//   hexa bench/bench.hexa --cells 512
//   hexa bench/bench.hexa --v3-gate              # v3.0 gate (hire_sim + phi_holo)
//   hexa bench/bench.hexa --phi-holo [--samples N] # phi_holo standalone measurement

